title: Meme Trading Continues Rolling On
itunes:title: Meme Trading Continues Rolling On
description:
Bloomberg Intelligence Senior Technology Analyst Mandeep Singh breaks down Qualcomm earnings. Bloomberg News Investing Reporter Annie Massa discusses her Bloomberg Businessweek story Just When You Think YOLO Trading Is Done, a New Meme Comes Along. And We Drive to the Close with Hilary Kramer, President and CIO at A&G Capital.

Hosts: Carol Massar and Tim Stenovec. Producer: Paul Brennan.
